674665%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Atlantic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bcongenital%20deficit%20worrier%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20has%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20long-term%20forecast%20is%20going%20to%20be%20way%20uncertain%2C%26quot%3B%20Summers%20said%20of%20deficits.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20probability%20is%20that%20we're%20on%20a%20completely%20unsustainable%20path.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Great%20Financial%20Crisis%2C%20he%20was%20among%20the%20top%20voices%20in%20the%20Obama%20administration%20to%20support%20federal%20deficit%20spending%20to%20jump%20start%20the%20economy%20and%20avoid%20long-term%20stagnation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20that%20era%20was%20characterized%20by%20deficit%20hawks%2C%20they%20were%20largely%20silent%20as%20deficits%20deepened%20during%20the%20Trump%20administration%20after%20Republican%20cut%20taxes%20without%20cutting%20spending%2C%20with%20outlays%20expanding%20further%20for%20COVID-related%20stimulus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20entitlement%20spending%20continues%20to%20rise%20as%20the%20population%20ages%2C%20with%20outlays%20for%20Social%20Security%20and%20Medicare%20now%20topping%20their%20dedicated%20revenue%20streams%20by%20%24500%20billion%20a%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Atlantic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20deficits%20add%20to%20the%20growing%20pile%20of%20US%20debt%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20servicing%20those%20obligations%20is%20going%20up%20along%20with%20the%20rise%20in%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Summers%2C%20there's%20no%20reason%20the%20government%20should%20continue%20to%20run%20massive%20deficits%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20economy%20is%20growing%20at%20a%20healthy%20pace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20deficits%20are%20also%20stoking%20inflation%20and%20forcing%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20to%20keep%20pumping%20up%20its%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20there's%20ever%20been%20a%20moment%20when%20the%20trajectory%20looks%20nearly%20as%20ominous%20as%20it%20does%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20citing%20current%20high%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20risking%20stagflation%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20investor%20interest%20in%20American%20assets%2C%20higher%20borrowing%20reduces%20investment%20relative%20to%20consumption%2C%20Summers%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20become%20more%20of%20an%20of-the-moment%20society%3B%20that%20goes%20for%20everything%20from%20inadequately%20funding%20Head%20Start%20to%20having%20insufficient%20investment%20for%20venture%20capital%2C%20to%20having%20inadequately%20trained%20armed%20forces%20and%20inadequately%20numerous%20forces%2C%20to%20doing%20too%20little%20investment%20to%20maintain%20leadership%20in%20AI%20and%20biomedicine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flarry-summers-deficits-unsustainable-debt-costs-medicare-medicaid-social-security-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689186209000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6061e06e8f71c3001853ac3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Flarry-summers-deficits-unsustainable-debt-costs-medicare-medicaid-social-security-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAny%20long-term%20forecast%20is%20going%20to%20be%20way%20uncertain.%20But%20the%20probability%20is%20that%20we're%20on%20a%20completely%20unsustainable%20path.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40insider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Flarry-summers-deficits-unsustainable-debt-costs-medicare-medicaid-social-security-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shell-hungry%20artillery%20battles%2