f%20corrupt%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%20data-cards%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%E2%80%94The%20Recount%20(%40therecount)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmims%2Fstatuses%2F1679146198517665793%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaetz's%20reference%20to%20Hoover%2C%20whom%20the%20FBI's%20headquarters%20are%20named%20after%2C%20harkens%20back%20to%20the%20controversial%20figure's%20nearly%20half-century%20running%20the%20bureau.%20Hoover's%20legacy%20is%20tarnished%20by%20the%20FBI's%20surveillance%20of%20political%20groups%20and%20civil%20rights%20activists%2C%20illegal%20probes%20of%20politicians%2C%20and%20other%20wrongdoing%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Fmagazine%2Farchive%2F2022%2F12%2Fj-edgar-hoover-fbi-influence%2F671900%2F%5C%22%3Eas%20The%20Atlantic%20once%20recounted.%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%20one%20of%20the%20most%20famous%20instances%2C%20the%20bureau%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2021%2F01%2F18%2F956741992%2Fdocumentary-exposes-how-the-fbi-tried-to-destroy-mlk-with-wiretaps-blackmail%5C%22%3Etried%20to%20destroy%20Martin%20Luther%20King%20Jr.%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20mailing%20the%20civil%20rights%20icon%20an%20anonymous%20note%20urging%20him%20to%20kill%20himself%20along%20with%20tapes%20of%20some%20of%20his%20extramarital%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Florida%20Republican%20snapped%20back%20after%20Wray%20pointed%20out%20the%20recruitment%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20deeply%20proud%20of%20them%2C%20and%20they%20deserve%20better%20than%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaetz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolling%20has%20shown%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F402464%2Fgovernment-agency-ratings-cia-fbi-federal-reserve-down.aspx%5C%22%3Ewhile%20close%20to%20a%20majority%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Americans%20approve%20of%20the%20FBI%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2023%2F03%2F30%2Famericans-feel-favorably-about-many-federal-agencies-especially-the-park-service-postal-service-and-nasa%2F%5C%22%3Ethere%20is%20a%20massive%20split%20between%20Democratic%20and%20Republicans.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20split%20coincidences%20with%20years%20of%20conservative%20attacks%20on%20the%20bureau.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWray%20volleyed%20repeated%20questions%20from%20Republican%20lawmakers%20about%20the%20FBI's%20handling%20of%20its%20January%206%20investigation%2C%20Hunter%20Biden's%20laptop%2C%20and%20other%20actions%20it%20has%20taken%20during%20the%20Biden%20administration.%20The%20bureau%20is%20also%20at%20the%20center%20of%20a%20special%20select%20panel%20on%20lawmakers%20probing%20the%20%26quot%3Bweaponization%20of%20the%20federal%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20a%20Democratic%20lawmaker%20pointed%20that%20it%20was%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20who%20appointed%20Wray%20to%20the%20top%20job%20after%20he%20fired%20Director%20James%20Comey.%20Wray%20then%20correctly%20recalled%20that%20only%20five%20senators%20voted%20against%20his%20confirmation.%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.senate.gov%2Flegislative%2FLIS%2Froll_call_votes%2Fvote1151%2Fvote_115_1_00181.htm%23position%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThey%20were%20all%20Democrats.%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaetz%20began%20his%20aggressive%20line%20of%20questioning%20by%20pointing%20to%20an%20alleged%20Hunter%20Biden%20%26quot%3Bshakedown%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20reference%20to%20an%20alleged%202017%20text%20Hunter%20Biden%20sent%20to%20a%20Chinese%20business%20partner%20that%20claimed%20he%20was%20sitting%20right%20next%20to%20the%20then-former%20Vice%20President.%20(Biden%20has%20since%20denied%20that%20he%20was%20present.)%20When%20Wray%20refused%20to%20characterize%20the%20text%2C%20Gaetz%20pressed%20if%20the%20director%20was%20%26quot%3Bprotecting%20the%20Bidens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20moved%20on%20to%20questions%20about%20a%20once-secret%20Foreign%20Intelligence%20Surveillance%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fjustice-department-fbi-surveillance-75c466a64e838ab12eaef96f6335f3cd%5C%22%3Ethat%20found%20the%20FBI%20had%20broken%20its%20own%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20conducting%20improper%20searches%20about%20January%206%20and%20Black%20Lives%20Matter%20protestors.%20Gaetz%20pointed%20out%20that%20Wray%20had%20previously%20testified%20before%20the%20Senate%20that%20to%20his%20knowledge%20the%20FBI%20had%20not%20relied%20on%20a%20database%20of%20foreign%20intelligence%20information%20in%20regard%20to%20its%20January%206%20investigation.%20The%20court's%20order%20found%20the%20FBI%20had%20done%20exactly%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20certainly%20didn't%20perjure%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Wray%20shot%20back%20Gaetz%2C%20who%20had%20accused%20him%20of%20lying%20to%20lawmakers.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20time%20I%20was%20testifying%20before%20the%20Senate%20Judiciary%20Committee%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20access%20to%20that%20piece%20of%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-director-florida-recruitment-up-over-100-percent-matt-gaetz-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689183992000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5a67a6fc00d0ef79008b4d50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-director-florida-recruitment-up-over-100-percent-matt-gaetz-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gaetz%2C%20a%20Florida%20Republican%2C%20tore%20into%20FBI%20Director%20Christopher%20Wray%20over%20his%20handling%20of%20the%20January%206%20investigation%20and%20other%20matters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%