%20John%20Gress%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20economy%20is%20in%20a%20rolling%20financial%20crisis%2C%20GMO's%20James%20Montier%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20paper.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMontier%20pointed%20to%20rising%20debt%20in%20the%20US%2C%20with%20the%20ratio%20of%20private%20debt%20to%20GDP%20above%20150%25%20for%20most%20of%20the%20last%2020%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThat%20could%20spell%20trouble%20as%20the%20US%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20tipping%20into%20recession%2C%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20economy%20is%20in%20the%20throes%20of%20a%20slow-moving%20financial%20crisis%20thanks%20to%20ballooning%20amounts%20of%20debt%20being%20racked%20up%20in%20the%20US%20private%20sector%2C%20according%20to%20GMO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20seem%20to%20live%20in%20an%20era%20of%20rolling%20financial%20crisis.%20I%20suspect%20this%20is%20the%20result%20of%20a%20massive%20build-up%20of%20private%20sector%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20GMO%20partner%20James%20Montier%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gmo.com%2Famericas%2Fresearch-library%2Fslow-burn-minsky-moments_whitepaper%2F%3Futm_medium%3Demail%26utm_source%3Depiserver-campaign%26utm_campaign%3Darticle-subscription-push%26utm_content%3DWhite-Paper%26email%3Djsor%2540insider.com%26first_name%3DJennifer%26last_name%3DS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhitepaper%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BSometimes%20these%20build-ups%20are%20accompanied%20by%20very%20high%20rates%20of%20credit%20growth%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20a%20credit%20bubble.%20On%20other%20occasions%20these%20builds-ups%20sit%20simmering%20in%20the%20background%2C%20largely%20unnoticed%20until%20the%20proverbial%20s**t%20hits%20the%20fan%2C%20when%20they%20suddenly%20act%20as%20an%20amplifier%20causing%20a%20much%20steeper%20decline%20than%20would%20otherwise%20have%20been%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMontier%20believed%20the%20second%20scenario%20describes%20most%20financial%20markets%20today%2C%20with%20private%20debt%20levels%20ballooning%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20But%20it's%20at%20particular%20risk%20of%20happening%20in%20the%20US%2C%20he%20warned%2C%20where%20the%20ratio%20of%20private%20sector%20debt%20to%20GDP%20has%20been%20north%20of%20150%25%20for%20most%20of%20the%20last%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20five-year%20private%20credit%20growth%20has%20remained%20relatively%20low%2C%20which%20suggests%20the%20US%20isn't%20yet%20in%20a%20credit%20bubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20mountain%20of%20private%20debt%20poses%20a%20threat%20to%20financial%20stability%20and%20to%20asset%20prices%2C%20especially%20considering%20other%20macro%20headwinds%20that%20are%20beating%20down%20on%20the%20economy.%20Some%20experts%20have%20warned%20of%20a%20recession%20to%20soon%20hit%2C%20thanks%20to%20high%20interest%20rates%20overtightening%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20imagine%20the%20US%20enters%20a%20recession%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20something%20the%20lead%20indicators%20are%20telling%20us%20the%20US%20is%20already%20experiencing.%20In%20this%20scenario%2C%20the%20cash%20flows%20of%20the%20private%20sector%20are%20likely%20to%20fall%20significantly%2C%20easily%20turning%20a%20run-of-the-mill%20recession%20into%20something%20far%20more%20unpleasant.%20This%20is%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20systemic%20risk%20embedded%20in%20our%20economics%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Montier%20warned%2C%20advising%20investors%20to%20choose%20assets%20that%20hedge%20against%20risk%20and%20serve%20as%20a%20store%20of%20value.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20market%20observers%20have%20also%20warned%20of%20a%20potential%20crisis%20to%20hit%20the%20US%20economy.%20GMO%20co-founder%20Jeremy%20Grantham%20has%20been%20sounding%20the%20alarm%20on%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fjeremy-grantham-stock-superbu