orating%20AI%20in%20their%20business%20models%2C%20such%20as%20firms%20like%20Deere%2C%20Interactive%20Brokers%2C%20and%20Humana.%20That's%20largely%20due%20to%20four%20concerns%20that%20make%20more%20%26quot%3Bobvious%26quot%3B%20AI%20trades%20like%20hardware%20and%20services%20less%20appealing%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E1.%20Inflation%20and%20interest%20rates%20are%20set%20to%20stay%20higher%20for%20the%20long-term.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20no%20longer%20operating%20in%20an%20era%20of%20easy%20money%2C%20where%20inflation%20stays%20close%20to%20the%20Fed's%202%25%20price%20target%20and%20near-zero%20interest%20rates%20facilitate%20cheap%20borrowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20stocks%20are%20priced%20today%20for%20a%20rapidly%20fading%20world%20of%202%25%20bond%20yields%2C%20low%20costs%20of%20capital%2C%20easy%20globalization%2C%20and%20friendly%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20strategists%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20a%20structural%20shift%20to%20higher%20inflation%20and%20interest%20rates%20over%20time%2C%20from%20the%20'2%25'%20world%20of%20the%20past%20two%20decades%20to%20a%20'5%25%20world'%20typical%20of%20the%20last%20hundred%20years%20of%20market%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E2.%20Limited%20upside.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20a%20third%20of%20AI%20firms%20on%20the%20market%20are%20unprofitable%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%20estimated.%20That's%20about%20double%20the%20proportion%20of%20unprofitable%20companies%20in%20the%20Nasdaq%20100%2C%20wherein%20just%2015%25%20of%20firms%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20pull%20a%20net%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20successful%20companies%20in%20the%20AI%20space%20may%20have%20limited%20upside.%20Nvidia%20stock%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20already%20trades%20around%2040%20times%20its%20revenue%2C%20while%20C3.ai%20trades%20around%2016%20times%20its%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20AI%20fund%20is%20also%20valued%2031%20times%20its%20forward%20earnings%20estimates%2C%20the%20bank%20said%2C%20which%20is%20around%201.7%20times%20the%20ratio%20seen%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20and%201.2%20times%20the%20ratio%20seen%20in%20the%20Nasdaq%20Composite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E3.%20AI%20stocks%20have%20seen%20high%20inflows%20at%20high%20prices.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20have%20continued%20to%20pour%20their%20cash%20into%20popular%20AI%20contenders.%20That%20could%20signal%20that%20the%20sector%20is%20overvalued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20ETFs%20saw%20%243.5%20billion%20of%20inflows%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20with%20just%20%241.1%20billion%20bought%20below%20%26quot%3Bcurrent%20breakeven%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20strategists%20said.%20Meanwhile%2C%2055%25%20of%20fund%20managers%20saw%20large-cap%20tech%20stocks%20as%20the%20most%20overcrowded%20trade%2C%20per%20Bank%20of%20America's%20Fund%20Manager%20Survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E4.%20There%20are%20barriers%20to%20AI%20development.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20obstacles%20that%20stand%20in%20the%20way%20for%20the%20improvement%20of%20AI%20technology.%20Large%20language%20models%20like%20ChatGPT%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20are%20using%20more%20energy%20and%20data%20to%20train.%20That%20could%20eventually%20lead%20to%20lower-quality%20data%20being%20fed%20to%20AI%20models%2C%20the%20bank%20said%2C%20particularly%20if%20firms%20are%20stingy%20with%20the%20information%20they%20provide%20to%20protect%20company%20secrets%2C%20or%20governments%20impose%20tighter%20regulation%20on%20AI%20bots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20be%20worsened%20by%20the%20US's%20new%20export%20curb%20to%20China%20for%20computer%20chips%20and%20chip%20manufacturing%20equipment%2C%20the%20bank%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-stocks-artificial-intelligence-investing-productivity-boom-economy-bofa-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689178905000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2