as%20because%20they%20didn't%20want%20to%20feel%20left%20out.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Dazeley%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFinancial%20differences%20are%20driving%20some%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20millennials%20to%20break%20up%20with%20their%20%26quot%3Bspendy%20friends.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOver%20a%20third%20of%20these%20consumers%20said%20friends%20led%20them%20to%20overspend%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.creditkarma.com%2Fabout%2Fcommentary%2Fgen-z-and-millennials-are-losing-friends-over-money-study-finds%5C%22%3Ea%20Credit%20Karma%20study%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERespondents%20said%20they%20felt%20pressured%20to%20overspend%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20FOMO%2C%20or%20fear%20of%20missing%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFriendships%20can%20end%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20reasons%20%E2%80%94%20and%20money%20can%20be%20a%20big%20reason.%20Disparate%20spending%20habits%20are%20leading%20some%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennial%20consumers%20to%20break%20up%20with%20their%20friends%2C%20a%20recent%20study%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20third%20of%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennial%20consumers%20reported%20having%20a%20friend%20who%20leads%20them%20to%20spend%20beyond%20what%20they%20can%20afford%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.creditkarma.com%2Fabout%2Fcommentary%2Fgen-z-and-millennials-are-losing-friends-over-money-study-finds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Credit%20Karma%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20by%20Qualtrics.%20The%20study%2C%20which%20ran%20from%20June%207%20to%20June%209%2C%20asked%20over%201%2C000%20US%20adults%20over%2018%20about%20their%20spending%20habits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20starting%20to%20lose%20friends%20over%20misaligned%20spending%20habits%2C%20it's%20really%20time%20to%20just%20level%20set%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20said%20Courtney%20Alev%2C%20director%20of%20product%20management%20and%20a%20consumer%20financial%20advocate%20at%20Credit%20Karma.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20keep%20your%20finances%20and%20your%20friendships%20in%20order.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20young%20consumers%20are%20overspending%3F%20Respondents%20chalked%20up%20part%20of%20their%20spending%20habits%20to%20FOMO%2C%20or%20fear%20of%20missing%20out.%20Over%2030%25%20of%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennial%20respondents%20said%20the%20main%20reason%20they%20overspent%20alongside%20their%20wealthier%20friends%20was%20because%20they%20didn't%20want%20to%20feel%20left%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20spending%20habits%20are%20drawing%20some%20consumers%20into%20debt.%20Eighty-eight%20percent%20of%20millennials%20and%2080%20percent%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20said%20spending%20time%20with%20these%20friends%20resulted%20in%20them%20taking%20on%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20think%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20that%20on%20your%20finances%2C%20especially%20with%20interest%20rates%20really%20high%20right%20now%2C%20going%20into%20debt%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20your%20friends%20is%20just%20really%20stressful%20on%20multiple%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20Alev%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20overspending%20drove%20these%20consumers%20into%20over%20%24500%20in%20debt%20%E2%80%94%20and%20prompted%20some%20to%20consider%20calling%20it%20quits%20with%20their%20%26quot%3Bspendy%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20found.%20Among%20those%20who%20said%20their%20friends%20lead%20them%20to%20spend%20more%2C%2047%25%20of%20millennials%20and%2036%25%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20said%20they%20were%20considering%20ending%20these%20friendships%20due%20to%20their%20different%20spending%20flexibility%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20survey%2C%20dining%20out%20accounts%20for%20much%20of%20the%20overspending.%20Forty-three%20percent%20of%20millennials%20said%20they%20overspent%20on%20dining%20out%2C%20as%20did%2037%25%20of%20Gen%20Zers.%20In%20addition%2C%2037%25%20of%20millennials%20and%2032%25%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20report%20overspending%20on%20drinks%20and%20nights%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20a%20third%20of%20Gen%20Z%20consumers%2C%2036%25%2C%20also%20said%20they%20overspent%20on%20clothing.%20%3Cs%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22strike%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fs%3EStudies%20have%20found%20that%20Gen%20Zers%2C%20people%20born%20between%201997%20and%202012%2C%20are%20particularly%20interested%20in%20spending%20chunks%20of%20their%20income%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-millennials-buying-driving-luxury-market-bain-study-2022-11%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-millennials-buying-driving-luxury-market-bain-study-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Eluxury%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-fast-fashion-cheap-clothes-tiktok-live-shopping-addiction-2023-5%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-fast-fashion-cheap-clothes-tiktok-live-shopping-addiction-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Efast%20fashion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20groups%20also%20attributed%20part%20of%20their%20overspending%20to%20expenses%20for%20trips%20and%20vacations.%20While%2021%25%20of%20millennials%20attributed%20some%20of%20their%20overspending%20to%20birthday%20celebrations%2C%2020%25%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20said%20they%20also%20overspent%20on%20self%20care%20expenses%2C%20such%20as%20massages%20and%20manicures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20avoid%20overspending%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAvoiding%20money%20problems%20coming%20between%20you%20and%20your%20friends%2C%20boils%20down%20to%20communication.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20money%20can%