%20for%20the%20Imphal%20West%20district%2C%20822%20personnel%20have%20been%20deployed%3B%20298%20personnel%20for%20Imphal%20East%3B%20236%20personnel%20for%20Bishnupur%3B%20147%20personnel%20for%20Thoubal%3B%20204%20personnel%20for%20Kakching%3B%20200%20personnel%20for%20Kangpokpi%20and%20300%20personnel%20for%20Churachandpur%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20informed%20that%20while%20conducting%20search%20operations%2C%20the%20state%20police%20and%20central%20forces%20destroyed%20two%20more%20bunkers%2C%20and%20recovered%20six%20more%20arms%20from%20the%20Imphal%20East%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-gun-licenses-biren-singh-violence%5C%22%3EExclusive%3A%20In%20Past%207%20Years%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20Govt%20Has%20Issued%20Highest%20Number%20of%20Gun%20Licences%20in%20Northeast%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20also%20informed%20that%20about%20127%20nakas%2Fcheckpoints%20were%20installed%20in%20different%20districts%20of%20Manipur%2C%20both%20in%20the%20hill%20and%20the%20valley.%20It%20added%20that%20298%20persons%20were%20detained%20in%20connection%20with%20violations%20in%20different%20districts%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20hundreds%20of%20women%20of%20Koirengei%20Awang%20village%20area%20on%20July%2011%20staged%20a%20protest%20against%20the%20authorities%20for%20sending%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20personnel%20to%20provide%20security%20to%20farmers%20during%20agricultural%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20personnel%20have%20been%20sent%20in%20Tingri%2C%20Khongnangpokpi%2C%20Chirik%20Loitong%20and%20Mapao%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protesters%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fmanipur-unrest-security-arrangement-for-farmers-draws-backlash%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EImphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20during%20a%20recent%20public%20meeting%2C%20a%20decision%20was%20made%20to%20disallow%20any%20central%20forces%2C%20and%20allow%20only%20state%20forces%2C%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20farmers%20and%20paddy%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNumerous%20farmers%20and%20villagers%20who%20went%20to%20the%20fields%20for%20farming%20activities%20have%20been%20seriously%20injured%20from%20gun%20attacks%20by%20the%20Kuki%20militants%20and%20hence%2C%20the%20committee%2C%20along%20with%20the%20villagers%2C%20had%20made%20demands%20to%20authorities%20concerned%20to%20deploy%20state%20forces%20in%20the%20area%20so%20that%20normal%20farming%20activities%20can%20continue%2C%E2%80%9D%20Koirengei%20Awang%20Village%20Development%20Committee%20president%20Hijam%20Priyokumar%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20villagers%20were%20apprehensive%20to%20work%20in%20their%20paddy%20fields%20even%20if%20the%20BSF%20were%20stationed%20because%20of%20their%20non-retaliatory%20operational%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fear%20of%20BSF%20just%20spectating%20while%20the%20Kuki%20militants%20attack%20is%20the%20biggest%20apprehension%20of%20the%20people%3B%20there%20is%20no%20use%20for%20such%20forces%20in%20the%20area%2C%20instead%2C%20exchange%20them%20with%20few%20state%20forces%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689174915000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F01132506%2FAgriculture_main.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fas-farming-starts-in-manipur-amid-tight-security-protesters-decry-deployment-of-central-forces%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20a%20recent%20public%20meeting%2C%20a%20decision%20was%20made%20to%20disallow%20any%20central%20forces%2C%20and%20allow%20only%20state%20forces%2C%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20farmers%20and%20paddy%20fields.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fr