indianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news-technology%2Fgst-on-online-gaming-india-inc-reaction-8830242%2F%5C%22%3Eimpose%20a%2028%25%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20online%20gaming%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20will%20wipe%20out%20the%20entire%20Indian%20gaming%20industry%20and%20lead%20to%20job%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST)%20Council%20on%20July%2011%20decided%20to%20levy%20a%20uniform%2028%25%20tax%20on%20full%20face%20value%20for%20online%20gaming%2C%20casinos%20and%20horse-racing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-economics%2F28-per-cent-tax-online-gaming-gst-council-8830353%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20the%20Monsoon%20Session%20of%20parliament%2C%20the%20government%20will%20bring%20in%20amendments%20to%20the%20GST-related%20laws%20to%20include%20online%20gaming%20and%20horse%20racing%20in%20Schedule%20III%20as%20taxable%20actionable%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20actionable%20claim%2C%20under%20the%20GST%2C%20is%20defined%20as%20goods%20under%20the%20Central%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20Act%2C%202017.%20So%20far%2C%20lottery%2C%20betting%2C%20and%20gambling%20were%20classified%20as%20actionable%20claims.%20Now%2C%20horse%20racing%20and%20online%20gaming%20will%20be%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20GST%20Council%20meeting%2C%20state%20finance%20ministers%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20the%20growing%20addiction%20to%20online%20gaming%2C%20especially%20among%20children%2C%20the%20newspaper%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20a%20decision%20to%20levy%20a%20uniform%20tax%20of%2028%25%20on%20full%20face%20value%20for%20online%20gaming%2C%20horse-racing%20and%20casinos%20was%20taken%20in%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20industry%20bodies%20%E2%80%93%20All%20India%20Gaming%20Federation%2C%20E-Gaming%20Federation%20and%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Fantasy%20Sports%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Ftechnology%2Fnews%2Fstory%2Fashneer-grover-startups-founders-enter-politics-slams-govt-28-per-cent-tax-online-gaming-2405282-2023-07-12%5C%22%3Ehave%20issued%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20joint%20statement%20saying%20that%20the%20tax%20may%20be%20levied%20on%20a%20total%20pool%20(prize%20money%20pooled%20plus%20the%20platform%20commission)%20and%20not%20on%20gross%20gaming%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20latter%20is%20implemented%2C%20it%20will%20mean%20the%20demise%20of%20the%20online%20skill%20gaming%20industry%20in%20India%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticising%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20Ashneer%20Grover%2C%20founder%20of%20BharatPe%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Ftime-for-startups-founders-to-enter-politics-and-be-represented-ashneer-grover%2Farticleshow%2F101694529.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20move%20will%20destroy%20India%E2%80%99s%20booming%20gaming%20sector%2C%20and%20that%20tech%20startup%20founders%20must%20enter%20politics%20for%20their%20voices%20to%20be%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrover%20has%20his%20pwn%20gaming%20startup%20called%20Crickpe%2C%20a%20fantasy%20cricket%20mobile%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRIP%20%E2%80%93%20Real%20money%20gaming%20industry%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Ftopic%2Findia%5C%22%3EIndia%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20the%20govt%20is%20thinking%20people%20will%20put%20in%20Rs100%20to%20play%20on%20Rs72%20pot%20entry%20(28%25%20Gross%20GST)%3B%20and%20if%20they%20win%20Rs%2054%20(after%20platform%20fees)-%20they%20will%20pay%2030%25%20TDS%20on%20that%20%E2%80%93%20for%20which%20they%20will%20get%20a%20free%20swimming%20pool%20in%20their%20living%20room%20come%20to%20the%20first%20monsoon%20%E2%80%93%20not%20happening!%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ERIP%20%E2%80%93%20Real%20money%20gaming%20industry%20in%20India.%20If%20the%20govt%20is%20thinking%20people%20will%20put%20in%20%E2%82%B9100%20to%20play%20on%20%E2%82%B972%20pot%20entry%20(28%25%20Gross%20GST)%3B%20and%20if%20they%20win%20%E2%82%B954%20(after%20platform%20fees)-%20they%20will%20pay%2030%25%20TDS%20on%20that%20%E2%80%93%20for%20which%20they%20will%20get%20free%20swimming%20pool%20in%20their%20living%20room%20come%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ashneer%20Grover%20(%40Ashneer_Grover)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAshneer_Grover%2Fstatus%2F1678790046537895937%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20implementation%20of%20a%2028%25%20tax%20rate%20will%20bring%20significant%20challenges%20to%20the%20gaming%20industry.%20This%20higher%20tax%20burden%20will%20impact%20companies%E2%80%99%20cash%20flows%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aaditya%20Shah%2C%20chief%20operating%20officer%20at%20the%20gaming%20app%20IndiaPlays%2C%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20decision%20ignores%20over%2060%20years%20of%20settled%20legal%20jurisprudence%20and%20lumps%20online%20skill%20gaming%20with%20gambling%20activities.%20This%20decision%20will%20wipe%20out%20the%20entire%20Indian%20gaming%20industry%20and%20lead%20to%20lakhs%20of%20job%20losses%20and%20the%20only%20people%20benefitting%20from%20this%20will%20be%20anti-national%20illegal%20offshore%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20All%20India%20Gaming%20Federation%20(AIGF)%20CEO%20Roland%20Landers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Feconomy%2Fimplementation-of-28-gst-rate-will-bring-challenges-to-online-gaming-industry-11689091580915.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIGF%20represents%20companies%20like%20Nazara%2C%20GamesKraft%2C%20Zupee%20and%20Winzo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELanders%20added%20that%20the%20decision%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%20(and)%20irrational%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmrit%20Kiran%20Singh%2C%20chief%20strategy%20advisor%20to%20the%20founders%20of%20the%20skill-gaming%20firm%20Gameskraft%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Feurope%2F%3Furl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fwill-wipe-out-the-entire-industry-say-online-gaming-cos-after-gst-set-at-28-10940241.html%26classic%3Dtrue%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EMoneycontrol%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20move%20%E2%80%9Cnegates%20all%20the%20good%20work%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20government%20has%20done%20to%20support%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%E2%80%99s%20decision%20at%20the%20GST%20Council%20is%20not%20in%20national%20interest%20as%20it%20will%20destroy%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20successful%20companies%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20startup%20ecosystem.%20Unfortunately%2C%20it%20also%20appears%20to%20show%20that%20the%20different%20limbs%20of%20the%20government%20are%20not%20in%20sync%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20will%20only%20support%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20overseas%20gaming%20companies%20and%20encourage%20the%20Indian%20industry%20to%20migrate%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20approach%20leaves%20many%20feathers%20ruffled%2C%2028%25%20on%20total%20consideration%20is%20like%20imposing%20a%20sin-tax%20on%20online%20skill%20gamers%20akin%20to%20one%20on%20cigarettes%20and%20alcohol.%20This%20lacks%20merit%20and%20is%20devoid%20of%20rationale.%20Contrary%20to%20position%20adopted%20in%20several%20leading%20international%20jurisdictions%2C%20a%2028%25%20tax%20on%20online%20skill%20gaming%20is%20a%20new%20low%20made%20in%20GST%E2%80%99s%20history%20without%20a%20thought%20to%20how%20businesses%20would%20survive%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adarsh%20Somani%2C%20Partner%2C%20Economic%20Laws%20Practice%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%