ll%20go%20and%20bowl%2C%20but%20she%20thought%20probably%20I%20was%20just%20joking%2C%26quot%3B%20Kumble%20reminisced%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20JioCinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20she%20even%20took%20it%20seriously.%20What's%20he%20saying%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20former%20India%20captain%20said%20even%20after%20breaking%20his%20jaw%20he%20felt%20it%20was%20his%20responsibility%20to%20get%20some%20wickets%20for%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20when%20I%20went%20back%20to%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%20I%20saw%20Sachin%20bowling%20because%20he%20was%20the%20only%20guy%20in%20the%20team%20who%20could%20bowl%20and%20then%20Wavell%20Hinds%2C%20I%20think%20was%20playing%20I%20don't%20remember%20somebody%20else%20was%20batting%2C%26quot%3B%20Kumble%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20my%20chance.%20I%20have%20to%20go%20and%20get%20a%20couple%20of%20wickets.%20If%20we%20can%20get%20West%20Indies%20three%20or%20four%20down%2C%20end%20of%20day%20two%20or%20three.%20I%20think%20if%20you%20can%20get%20them%20out%2C%20then%20maybe%2C%20we%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20win%20the%20game.%20That%20was%20the%20only%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20told%20Andrew%20Leipus%20-%20get%20me%20out%20there.%26quot%3B%20Kumble%20was%20due%20to%20fly%20back%20to%20Bangalore%20the%20following%20day%20for%20surgery%2C%20and%20he%20said%20at%20that%20time%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20least%20I%20can%20now%20go%20home%20with%20the%20thought%20that%20I%20tried%20my%20best.%26quot%3B%20Batting%20at%20No.%207%2C%20Kumble%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20Mervyn%20Dillon%20short%20ball.%20He%20spat%20out%20blood%20but%20batted%20on%20for%20another%2020%20minutes%20in%20the%20fourth%20Test%20of%20that%20series%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20toughest%20batters%20he%20had%20bowled%20to%20during%20his%20illustrious%20career%2C%20he%20picked%20Lara%2C%20Saeed%20Anwar%2C%20Jacques%20Kallis%2C%20and%20Aravinda%20de%20Silva%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20I%20think%20it%20was%20good%20that%20most%20of%20them%20were%20a%20part%20of%20my%20team.%20Imagine%20bowling%20at%20Sachin%2C%20Rahul%2C%20Saurav%2C%20Viru%2C%20Laxman%2C%20all%20these%20guys%20in%20a%20match.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20a%20nightmare.%20Jokes%20apart%20had%20some%20wonderful%20batters%20whom%20I%20bowled%20against%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAravinda%20de%20Silva%20was%20a%20tough%20one%20and%20Brian%20Lara%20-%20he%20probably%20had%20three%20shots%20to%20every%20ball%20and%20he%20would%20change.%20You%20would%20think%20that%20you've%20got%20him.%26quot%3B%20On%20Lara%2C%20the%20only%20man%20to%20score%20400%20in%20Test%20cricket%2C%20he%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BYou'd%20feel%20that%20you've%20deceived%20it%20and%20then%20suddenly%20you%20play%20a%20shot%2C%20which%20you%20can't%20imagine%20and%20when%20you%20know%20that%20he's%20come%20forward%2C%20you%20have%20beaten%20him%2C%20and%20then%20he%20would%20just%20use%20the%20pace%20and%20then%20late%20cut%20for%20four%20and%20that%20was%20his%20quality.%26quot%3B%20Kumble%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20in%20every%20series%2C%20you%20sort%20of%20encounter%20a%20couple%20of%20tough%20guys%20who%20sort%20of%20are%20difficult.%20Jacques%20Kallis%20was%20someone%20who%20never%2C%20ever%20gave%20away%20his%20wicket.%20Inzi%20(Inzamam-Ul-Haq)%20was%20really%20tough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20I%20mean%20some%20of%20the%20left-handers%20were%20really%20-%20Hayden%20was%20someone%20who%20was%20imposing.%20We%20knew%20that%20getting%20him%20out%20LBW%20was%20out%20of%20the%20equation.%26quot%3B%20One%20of%20only%20three%20cricketers%20to%20have%20taken%20all%2010%20wickets%20in%20a%20Test%20match%20innings%2C%20Kumble%20said%20the%20thought%20that%20he%20could%20account%20for%20all%20the%20Pakistani%20batters%20during%20the%201999%20game%20in%20Delhi%20crossed%20his%20mind%20after%20he%20picked%20up%20his%20sixth%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20I%20think%20at%20the%20end%20of%20six%2C%20it%20was%20tea%20break.%20Yeah.%20So%2C%20I%20got%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20break%20and%20then%20seven%20happened.%20Saleem%20Malik%20got%20out%20of%20and%20then%20eight%20and%20nine%20happened%20in%20two%20deliveries%20off%20the%20fifth%20and%20the%20sixth%20ball%20so%20I%20knew%20that%2C%20okay%2C%20here's%20my%20chance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689169500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fksrv6tt8_anil-kumble-broken-jaw-2022-afp_625x300_12_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwife-thought-i-was-joking-anil-kumble-on-bowling-with-broken-jaw-4199643%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202002%2C%20Anil%20Kumble%20bowled%20with%20a%20bandaged%20face%20and%20a%20broken%20jaw%20against%20West%20Indies%20in%20Antigua.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwife-thought-i-was-joking-anil-kumble-on-bowling-with-broken-jaw-4199643%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwife-thought-i-was-joking-anil-kumble-on-bowling-with-broken-jaw-4199643%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwife-thought-i-was-joking-anil-kumble-on-bowling-with-broken-jaw-4199643%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SSR's%20privacy%20rights%20died%20with%20him%3A%20Delhi%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689168975000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101702827%2Cimgsize-1336966.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsushant-singh-rajputs-privacy-rights-died-with-him-delhi-hc-refuses-to-stay-streaming-of-film-nyaay-the-justice%2Farticleshow%2F101701295.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3