na%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20that%20Chinese%20travellers%20to%20the%20country%20should%20be%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20vigilant%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cbeware%20of%20falling%20into%20US%20snares%20and%20arrest-entrapment%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-warns-its-citizens-on-entrapment-by-us-law-enforcement%2Farticleshow%2F101661084.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-warns-its-citizens-on-entrapment-by-us-law-enforcement%2Famp_articleshow%2F101661084.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-warns-its-citizens-on-entrapment-by-us-law-enforcement%2Famp_articleshow%2F101661084.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20the%20Heroes%20Saving%20Lives%20as%20Himachal%20Battles%20Massive%20Floods%20%26%20Landslides%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENorth%20India%20experienced%20heavy%20rainfall%20in%20the%20past%20three%20days.%20The%20Indian%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20has%20issued%20warnings%20that%20more%20heavy%20downpour%20is%20expected%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Delhi%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F241059%2Fpostmaster-women-himachal-pradesh-gramin-dak-sevak-letter-pension-delivery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHimachal%20Pradesh%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20especially%2C%20has%20seen%20incessant%20rains%20leading%20to%20landslides%20and%20flash%20floods%2C%20leading%20to%20widespread%20destruction.%20All%20major%20rivers%20including%20Beas%2C%20Ravi%2C%20Chenab%2C%20and%20Satluj%20are%20in%20spate%2C%20as%20vehicles%2C%20bridges%2C%20shops%2C%20and%20houses%20are%20being%20swept%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C