%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%3A%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%F0%9F%9A%80LVM3-M4%2FChandrayaan-3%20%F0%9F%9B%B0%EF%B8%8FMission%3A%3Cbr%3EThe%20launch%20is%20now%20scheduled%20for%20%3Cbr%3E%F0%9F%93%86July%2014%2C%202023%2C%20at%202%3A35%20pm%20IST%20%3Cbr%3Efrom%20SDSC%2C%20Sriharikota%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EStay%20tuned%20for%20the%20updates!%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1676918082265321472%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-2%3A%20A%20stepping%20stone%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20416px)%20100vw%2C%20416px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchandrayaan2-1688735226.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22416%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20file%20image%20of%20Chandrayaan%202%20lift%20off%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchandrayaan2-1688735226.jpg%20416w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchandrayaan2-1688735226-199x300.jpg%20199w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fchandrayaan2-1688735226-150x226.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323088%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22626%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFile%20image%20of%20Chandrayaan%202%20lift-off%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20ISRO%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20is%20a%20follow-up%20to%20Chandrayaan-2%2C%20and%20a%20result%20of%20four%20years%20of%20efforts%20by%20ISRO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earlier%20mission%20was%20launched%20on%2022%20July%202019%20into%20space%20using%20the%20Geosynchronous%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark%20III.%20The%20project%20cost%20Rs%20978%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chandrayaan-2%20spacec