0and%20useful%20for%20tucking%20the%20forearm%20of%20the%20shooter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weapons%20were%20popular%20in%20the%20region%20of%20Khanate%20of%20Kalat%2C%20which%20historically%20corresponds%20to%20the%20modern-day%20Balochistan%20province%20of%20Pakistan.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20Mughal%20subjects%2C%20these%20fierce%20leaders%20and%20their%20tribes%20were%20descendants%20of%20the%20ethnic%20pastoralists%20of%20the%20region%20called%20Brahuis%2C%20after%20the%20language%20they%20spoke.%20The%20men%20typically%20wore%20their%20hair%20long%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20writes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Amrita%20Sher%E2%80%93Gil%20and%20Indira%E2%80%93Sher%20Gil%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fa554262da81b45bdbd7bb4eedf578ffe_338410372_922187872152427_1671031433945797450_n-1688730762.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amrita%20Sher%20Gil%20is%20also%20known%20as%20the%20pioneer%20of%20modern%20Indian%20art%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fa554262da81b45bdbd7bb4eedf578ffe_338410372_922187872152427_1671031433945797450_n-1688730762.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fa554262da81b45bdbd7bb4eedf578ffe_338410372_922187872152427_1671031433945797450_n-1688730762-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fa554262da81b45bdbd7bb4eedf578ffe_338410372_922187872152427_1671031433945797450_n-1688730762-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fa554262da81b45bdbd7bb4eedf578ffe_338410372_922187872152427_1671031433945797450_n-1688730762-768x960.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fa554262da81b45bdbd7bb4eedf578ffe_338410372_922187872152427_1671031433945797450_n-1688730762-150x188.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323046%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAmrita%20Sher%20Gil%20is%20also%20known%20as%20the%20pioneer%20of%20modern%20Indian%20art%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Deepthi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Deepthi%20points%20out%2C%20one%20of%20the%20learnings%20that%20she%20has%20acquired%20through%20her%20tryst%20with%20museums%20is%20that%20tiny%20bits%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F320476%2Fhistory-and-origin-of-chhurpi-worlds-hardest-cheese-northeast-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esartorial%20history%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20survive%20in%20the%20cracks%20of%20our%20society%20are%20incredible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20strides%20in%20photography%20made%20by%20the%20Lumiere%20Brothers.%20It%20is%20a%20well-known%20fact%20that%20the%20autochrome%20technique%20%E2%80%94%20a%20colour%20photography%20process%20popular%20in%20the%2019th%20century%20%E2%80%94%20was%20patented%20by%20the%20Lumiere%20brothers.%20It%20created%20an%20appeal%20among%20the%20people%20for%20its%20ability%20to%20produce%20coloured%20pictures.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Fhistory%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eduring%20her%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Deepthi%20came%20across%20a%20fact%20that%20continues%20to%20surprise%20her%20till%20date.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20autochrome%20plates%20had%20millions%20of%20tiny%20granules%20of%20potato%20starch%20coloured%20in%20the%20primary%20colours%20of%20red%2C%20blue%20and%20green!%E2%80%9D%20she%20exclaims.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20photograph%20here%20depicts%20this%20form%20of%20pho