l%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-2-1-1688732547.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-2-1-1688732547-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-2-1-1688732547-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-2-1-1688732547-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image-2-1-1688732547-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323070%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAn%20outdoor%20classroom%20in%20EuroSchool%20Bannerghatta.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Akanksha%20Gupta%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheetalakshmi%2C%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20school%2C%20believes%20that%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20bring%20the%20concept%20of%20sustainability%20to%20life.%20%E2%80%9CA%20sustainable%20world%2C%20filled%20with%20the%20blessings%20and%20bounty%20of%20nature%2C%20is%20the%20best%20gift%20we%20can%20leave%20behind%20for%20future%20generations.%20At%20school%20we%20subtly%20sensitise%20students%20about%20the%20environment%20through%20hands-on%20and%20thought-provoking%20activities%2C%20by%20incorporating%20them%20into%20their%20curriculum%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20students%20have%20been%20in%20awe%20of%20the%20place%20and%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20move%20around%20freely.%20They%20are%20given%20a%20scheduled%20time%20daily%20to%20have%20outdoor%20activities%2C%20have%20classroom%20sessions%20outside%20in%20the%20SOUL%20(School%20Outdoor%20Learning%20Hubs)%2C%20climb%20trees%20if%20they%20please%2C%20and%20enjoy%20fresh%20and%20clean%20air%20and%20sunlight.%20If%20they%20are%20learning%20about%20fruit-bearing%20trees%20then%20they%20can%20see%20those%20in%20real-time%20in%20the%20school%20which%20aids%20their%20learning%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaida%2C%20a%20student%20of%20Class%208%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20school%20is%20unlike%20any%20other%20school%20in%20the%20city.%20We%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20go%20outdoors%20and%20learn%20from%20nature.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20rainwater%20harvesting%20that%20we%20learn%20in%20books%20is%20right%20here%20in%20the%20school.%20We%20also%20plant%20our%20food%20near%20our%20cafeteria%2C%20which%20gives%20us%20an%20idea%20of%20where%20our%20food%20comes%20from%20and%20the%20hard%20work%20involved%20in%20growing%20food.%20I%20love%20how%20our%20teachers%20always%20give%20us%20the%20time%20to%20explore%20the%20surroundings.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Akanksha%20and%20Saurabh%20believe%20that%20the%20school%20takes%20a%20step%20forward%20while%20going%20back%20to%20the%20roots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20we%20can%20learn%20from%20nature%20and%20I%20believe%20that%20if%20given%20the%20opportunity%20the%20students%20will%20feel%20inspired%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F84622%2Fsubbaiah-bharathidasan-arulagam-saving-vultures-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreserve%20and%20protect%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20kids%20of%20the%20upcoming%20generation%20lack%20a%20connection%20with%20the%20wild%20and%20the%20school%20helps%20to%20forge%20that%20connection%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saurabh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688733767000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEuroschool-image--1688732294.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D323054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Built%20by%20architects%2